In the MATTER OF the License of Kevin MCCAFFERTY, A.P.N., R.N., R.N. #26NR04704300 A.P.N. #26NJ00276800 To Practice Nursing in the State of New Jersey. (Kevin McCafferty- Petitioner) C-900 September Term 2017
080435 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002141-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
